--// Functions 

--
MakeCategory(Name) - Returns a container and adds a category 
--

--
Title(Name) - update the title of the main window

MakeRow(Name, {Type, Value, Container}) - Returns a row 
Value - an optional ValueBase instance such as a boolvalue 
Container - a container from the MakeCategory function 
Type - a string that can be one of - {"Bool", "Button"} 
--

--
AddThread(Thread)

Adds a thread that should be able to disconnect, such as renderstepped events. When the UI is closed, these threads will disconnect.
local thread = RenderStepped:Connect()
AddThread(thread)
--


--// Other 

Converted - a table containing all of the UIs contents


